data.text:
This documentary from acclaimed filmmaker Emir Kusturica traces the life and times of Diego Maradona from his humble beginnings to worldwide fame. Released in 2008. Total length: 93 minutes.

This Region 2 PAL-format DVD is only suitable for use in the UK, Europe, Middle East, South Africa and Japan. Customers with 'chipped' PAL-compatible players in other Regions should also be able to view this DVD.
